<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">六　摩訶梨經</cb:mulu><ref cRef="PTS.D.1.158" type="PTS_hide"></ref>
<milestone unit="juan" n="7"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N06.0004.0175a" n="0175a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">七　闍利經</cb:mulu><head>七　闍利經</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a04"/><p xml:id="pN06p0175a0401"><ref cRef="PTS.D.1.159"></ref>一</p><p xml:id="pN06p0175a0402" style="margin-left:2em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">如是我聞。一時，世尊住憍賞彌之瞿師羅園。其時，普行者滿提左與持木鉢之
<lb ed="N" n="0175a05"/>弟子闍利，詣往世尊之處。詣已，共相問候致意，退立一面，如是言：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a06"/><p xml:id="pN06p0175a0601" style="margin-left:2em;text-indent:2em">「友！尊瞿曇！命與身是一、或是異耶？」</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a07"/><p xml:id="pN06p0175a0701" style="margin-left:2em;text-indent:2em">「然者，友！諦聽，善思念之，我當說。」</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a08"/><p xml:id="pN06p0175a0801" style="margin-left:2em;text-indent:2em">彼二出家者，應諾世尊曰：「友！唯然。」</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a09"/><p xml:id="pN06p0175a0901">二～五</p><p xml:id="pN06p0175a0904" style="margin-left:2em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">「友！如來出現於世，〔如來是〕應供者、正覺者……乃至……友！我如是
<lb ed="N" n="0175a10"/><ref cRef="PTS.D.1.160"></ref>知、如是見，不言：『命與身是一、或是異。』」〔同摩訶梨經一六～一九節，故略
<lb ed="N" n="0175a11"/>之。〕</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a12"/><p xml:id="pN06p0175a1201" style="margin-left:2em;text-indent:2em">世尊如是說已。彼等二出家者，歡喜世尊之所說。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a14"/>
